t said they had failed \\\"gender tests\\\".\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999990843493478, \"rank\": 9.156515930856495e-07, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The trigger\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcry\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"their disqualification\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous year's world championships\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"gender tests\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Y chromosome had been identified in two blood samples.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Y chromosome\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"two blood samples\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both women had been registered as female at birth but they had not met the female category eligibility criteria.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both women\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the female category eligibility criteria\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasmuch noise and little claritybut differences of sex development (DSD) describes a group of conditions that occur early in pregnancy in which sex development is not typical.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.9999573038432685, \"rank\": 4.2697979349908205e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333