ation\", \"from\": 8383, \"to\": 8397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the events have raised fresh doubts over Lin's ability to come back in the ring, as has World Boxing's announcement that they will establish a working group to reexamine its gender eligibility rules which is expected to report back in the early new year.\", \"from\": 8399, \"to\": 8657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8497, \"end\": 8503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.753099944219659e-24, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 8403, \"to\": 8413}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh doubts\", \"from\": 8426, \"to\": 8438}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin's ability\", \"from\": 8444, \"to\": 8457}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 8474, \"to\": 8482}, {\"ngram\": \"a working group\", \"from\": 8544, \"to\": 8559}, {\"ngram\": \"its gender eligibility rules\", \"from\": 8573, \"to\": 8601}, {\"ngram\": \"the early new year\", \"from\": 8638, \"to\": 8656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At World Boxing, we put boxers first and the safety of athletes is absolutely paramount,\\\" a spokesman said.\", \"from\": 8659, \"to\": 8767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World Boxing\", \"from\": 8663, \"to\": 8675}, {\"ngram\": \"boxers\", \"from\": 8684, \"to\": 8690}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 8701, \"to\": 8711}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 8715, \"to\": 8723}, {\"ngram\": \"a spokesman\", \"from\": 8750, \"to\": 8761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement inevitably also raises doubts that Khelif will be able to compete in the organisation's world championships in Liverpool in September, as the Algerian had suggested she would before turning pro.\", \"from\": 8768, \"to\": 8979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8896, \"end\": 8905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.988582730936